  "keyFeatures": [
    "Dynamic custom block creation using vanilla block states as proxies",
    "Custom item system with behaviors, models, and equipment support",
    "Furniture system with hitboxes, seats, and multi-part display entities",
    "Custom recipe support (shaped, shapeless, cooking, smithing, stonecutting, brewing)",
    "Automatic resource pack generation, optimization, and delivery",
    "Template system for reusable block states, models, and loot tables",
    "Premium resource pack obfuscation and protection features",
    "Java API with Bukkit events for plugin interoperability",
    "Folia support for multi-threaded servers",
    "Custom emoji/image rendering via Unicode font injection"
  ],
